Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThis sucker's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it in the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] It's a crate\Nfull of cannonballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I figured since we\Nhave our own cannon now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we could get in some\Ntarget practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP chuckles] Just leave\Nthe cannoning to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I harken back to the time I was\Nthree years old and jumped on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,a passing cannonball,\Nriding it halfway 'round...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSo how do you work this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! You know\Nhow to shoot this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Asleep.\NThe guy sleeps constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, just to the\Nsouth of here is a reef
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that would make for some\Nexcellent target practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For real, guys! What are\Nwe sitting around here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOOP chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "The Three-Sword Style's\NPast! Zoro and Kuina's Vow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody wanna come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to challenge your dojo.\NSend someone out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dojo challenge is quite a\Nrarity these days, young one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Heh. Don't count me\Nout just because I'm a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next village\Nover, I'm unrivaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very wll then. I accept\Nyour challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] And if I win,\Nthen I get your dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NAnd if you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I'll, uh... then I'll\Njoin this place. How 'bout that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NSounds very fair. Kuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS yelp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What is it, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you're not gonna\Nfight me yourself, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuina may be just a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's stronger than\Nany adult among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as her father, I can tell\Nyou this without prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come inside\Nthen and prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I use as many as I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NAll right. Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NBow before the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NWhat is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B]\NHe's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KUINA grunts]\N--[ZORO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you studied Two-Sword\Nstyle technique before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've\Neven held a bamboo sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really. Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Damn it!\NI'm strong, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna get even\Nstronger! I refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to lose to this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he ever heard of dodging?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NThis match is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA]\NHe's like a boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, Kuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an amateur. And he's ten\Nyears too early to even attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,using the Two-Sword style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitter? Because we can go\Nanother round if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]\NA loss is a loss, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER] It is wise to\Naccept defeat gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Now I'll be a student\Nhere. Got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWait. I want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna train day\Nafter day, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I'm gonna beat\Nyou. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That day will never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting, yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[INSTRUCTOR] Match over!\NAnd the winner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuina with 2,000 total\Nwins and zero losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO groaning]\NDamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA] You're weak, Zoro.\NNothing ever changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, for a boy,\Nyou're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Zoro isn't weak at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of the strongest\Nout of all the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C]\NHe's even beaten grownups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KUINA] But...\N--[STUDENTS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nowhere as strong as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with two swords, a\Nweakling is still a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You losers would do good to\Nremember that and keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your howling makes you\Nlook even more pitiful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,than you already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NYou've grown so strong, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you continue to lose\Nevery match against Kuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NSensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you giving her\Nspecial training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be your daughter,\Nbut that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. I've done\Nnothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Zoro has\Ngrown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Kuina has continued\Nto grow stronger as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NZoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B]\NZoro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI'm gonna go clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Damn it!\NWhy can't I beat Kuina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be the strongest\Nswordsman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So why can't I beat her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Tonight I\Nfight her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[NSTRUCTOR] It's only been a\Nyear since Zoro became a pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and the boy's progress is\Nnothing short of spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He trains so much more than the\Nother pupils, it's incomparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be what attributes\Nto his progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that the boy\Nis still no match for Kuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER] Female swordsmen\Nare faced with immense walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[INSTRUCTOR]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As she is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot trust the inheritance\Nof this dojo to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[INSTRUCTOR]\NKuina!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER] It's not polite\Nto eavesdrop, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become the world's\Ngreatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NKuina. As a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you can never become the\Nworld's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA]\NZoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late out.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny. I was gonna ask\Nyou the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come here\Nto challenge you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to your two thousand\Nand first fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's gonna be the last fight\Nyou and me will ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This ends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me with a real sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have one, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Real swords...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wado... Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, KUINA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, KUINA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA] Two real swords are\Nheavier than you thought, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See. You still lack strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO growls]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Win number 2,001.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks... I... I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA] I'm the one who should\Nbe crying out of frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When girls grow up, its\Nnatural for us to develop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,into physically weaker\Nbeings than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you will catch up\Nto me soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always heard\Nyou say to me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told my father\Nthe same thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he said I could never be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know. I know that. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky Zoro,\Nbeing born as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted was to be the\Nworld's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My breasts have even started to\Ngrow out now. If only...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had just been born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDon't fly off at the mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,whining like that\Nafter you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not fair!\NYou're my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how this\Nmakes me feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Boy this, girl that.\NAre you gonna keep up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that same kinda talk after\NI beat you some day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like skill is irrelevant!\NThat's just an insult to all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of the training I've been\Npouring on every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't say that\Ncrap, would ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me that someday\None of us will be
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll compete and\Nsee who gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy. You're so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA, ZORO]\NIt's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[INSTRUCTOR, KUINA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A] She's gotten\Neven stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I gotta get stronger\Nso I can hold lots of swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If two's not enough,\NI'll use three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat do you guys want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NKunia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuina is dead, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A]\NThey said she slipped
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and fell down the\Nstorehouse steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN B]\NStorehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A] Looking for a sharpening\Nstone for her beloved sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN B] What would\Nshe need that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A]\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN B]\NShe was just a child, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A] Who knows why\Nanyone does anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to\Nrationalize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN B] Guess ya never\Nknow what's waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,around the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO, FIGHTER A grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER] It may appear\Notherwise to the blind eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but people are quite\Nfragile things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuina... She was a\Nvery competitive girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,From the time she was old enough\Nto make a decision for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,she practiced in this Dojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,achieving strength that\Nsurpassed many adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was this fruition of power
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that caused her to\Nbecome a bit conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you appeared, Zoro.\NAnd I thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you\Ngrew ever stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuina felt compelled\Nto practice even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So as not to lose to you.\NSo as not to lose to a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Through this, she had\Nbegun to chip away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at the walls of female\Nswordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite any of which I speak,\NI am, above all other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,an ordinary parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And as any human,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am bound by my emotions\Nas well as my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at you now,\NZoro, I... feel only pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NSensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that you let\Nme have that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NKuina's sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI'll get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than she ever\Nwas, you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong enough that my name\Nreaches up to the Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised her. I promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NYes. The sword is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave her spirit and her\Ndreams in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO wails]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been eight years, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally going to\Nset out on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NYes, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To fulfill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOJO MASTER]\NTake care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat was way off the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, What's so loud down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannon firing practice!\NBut it's not going very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said... Let the\Nexpert aim the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the flying\Ndistance of the last one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Awesome! You hit\Nthat thing on the first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWow, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha think? I'm\Npretty magnificent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to aiming!\NSo, are you impressed yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You better believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's all settled.\NYou'll be our sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWait, I don't get to be captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo. I'm still the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZORO chuckles]\N--[USOPP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Whatever. I'll\Nhumor you for now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the second you do something\Ncowardly, I'm taking your post!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can live with that. But, you\Nknow guys, I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one other position\Nthat we have to fill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,before we can head out\Nfor the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. The kitchen\Nis really nice on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... pay me, and I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I suppose it is\Nvital for long trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] No decent pirate ship\Nshould be without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NAre you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] What do you think\Nwe're doing out here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Just when I thought you\Nwere gonna say something smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBut we're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Pirates sing a lot!\NDidn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NGet out here ya damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What the hell?\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] Shut up!\NWho I am means nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya stinkin' pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--[JOHNNY grunts]\N--[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, how many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... One.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just let him handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the years I've lost count\Nof all the pirate heads
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we've taken.\NAnd now you guys think...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you can kill my\Npartner?! [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm? That voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat do you mean by 'partner'?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look I don't know\Nwhat this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But just stop\Nwrecking our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NLost by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Johnny.\NTell me that isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Who's sayin' my name
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,like they think they\Nknow me or somethin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Big Bro Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NJohnny! It is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] What are you\Ndoin' here, big bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Where's Yosaku?\NIsn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys know each\Nother or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.84,0:24:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI suppose we need a cook now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I heard there's a\NSea Restaurant out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.15,0:24:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP screams]\NThe navy ship's firing on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo prob! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.90,0:24:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] The restaurant's\Nthe other way, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.70,0:24:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'll go apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat is taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.32,0:24:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Let's go check\Nit out and get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.03,0:24:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZORO] Another fight?!\N--[USOPP] What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.49,0:24:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.33,0:24:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Famous Cook! Sanji of\Nthe Sea Restaurant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.42,0:24:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates!

